    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You are looking at an absolute gem that\u2019s been pampered since day one. Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dings, and the interior is spotless\u2014it's basically perfection on wheels. I've taken such good care of this beauty, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
