    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-flow exhaust manifold. The drivetrain is paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, the double-VANOS system has been proactively overhauled, and the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced to ensure chassis integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping and aluminum control arms, preserving the car's celebrated turn-in response and minimal unsprung mass. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior exhibits zero clear coat degradation or panel misalignment. This is a turnkey, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist seeking a preserved icon of the analog era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
