      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory finish with zero stone chips or imperfections, having been strictly garage-kept under a soft cover. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the infotainment system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous full-service history and a drive that feels as tight and responsive as the day it left the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
